<Base
  title="Accepting Payments in Japan: The Complete Guide for SMEs : MKUltraman"
  description="How  to accept payments in Japan as an SME or foreign founder : credit cards, QR codes, bank transfer, convenience store payment, and how  to build a full Japan payment stack."
